==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pickthank
<hw>Pick"thank`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who strives to
put another under obligation; an officious person; hence, a flatterer.
Used also adjectively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Smiling <qex>pickthanks</qex>, and base newsmongers.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Picktooth</ent>⟦br⟧
